download and install conda
create new project with conda env, and choose as executable:
 C:\Users\michaelpiro1\AppData\Local\anaconda3\... find the path to conda.exe file

pip install -U git+https://github.com/facebookresearch/demucs#egg=demucs
pip uninstall torch
conda install pytorch==2.1.0 torchvision==0.16.0 torchaudio==2.1.0 pytorch-cuda=11.8 -c pytorch -c nvidia
run the script in the env





conda env update -f C:\Users\michaelpiro1\PycharmProjects\pythonProject\training\environment-cuda.yml # if you have GPUs
conda activate demucs
pip install -e .